For sure its hung?  You seem to be crawling wikipedia this time and in 
your last mail.  Is this all you are crawling?  If so, retries because 
of the below connection timeouts with the Heritrix increasing interval 
between retries may look like the crawler is hung.  Check the frontier 
report.  

Is there nothing in heritrix_out.log?  You could send the process a 
SIGQUIT signal -- $ kill -3 HERITRIX_PROCESS_ID -- and it&#39;ll send a 
thread dump to heritrix_out.log.  Study the output.  Wait a while.  
Redo. Compare the stack traces.  Any progress?  If none or you can&#39;t 
make sense of it, send it on over. Maybe we can see something in thread 
dump tea leaves.

St.Ack


